From: Andrea <auguccioni15@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 01 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] plat/st/stm32mp1: add .note.GNU-stack to stm32mp1_helper.S

binutils 2.40 treats the missing .note.GNU-stack section as a linker
warning, and TF-A builds with -Wl,--fatal-warnings, so the warning
becomes a fatal error when linking bl2.elf.

Add an explicit .note.GNU-stack section with %progbits to declare a
non-executable stack and silence the linker warning.

Signed-off-by: Andrea <auguccioni15@gmail.com>
---
 plat/st/stm32mp1/stm32mp1_helper.S | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/plat/st/stm32mp1/stm32mp1_helper.S b/plat/st/stm32mp1/stm32mp1_helper.S
--- a/plat/st/stm32mp1/stm32mp1_helper.S
+++ b/plat/st/stm32mp1/stm32mp1_helper.S
@@ -254,3 +254,5 @@ end_error_str:
 	.asciz "\n\r"
 #endif
+
+	.section	.note.GNU-stack,"",%progbits
